            <h2>Five Lessons</h2>

            <h3  style="padding-top: 15px">Growing Up</h3>
            <p>Growing up you experienced something that you never wish to revisit It could be the desperation of extreme poverty, the isolation of social rejection, or even the guilt associated with having done something wrong.</p>
            <p>
                What have you learned should be avoided at all costs? What measures do you take these days to avoid this?
            </p>
