            <br />

            <h3  style="padding-top: 15px">As a Child</h3>
            <p>When you were a child, someone close to you hid a truth from you. As an adult you realized that person's deception.</p>
            <p>
                How did the lie shape you? Did the truth hurt you? How do you approach deception as an adult?
            </p>
            <input name="flags.detailedcharinfo.fivelessons4" value="{{flags.detailedcharinfo.fivelessons4}}" id="FiveLessons4" type="text" maxlength="300" placeholder="eg. Chuk realized there are other creatures besides Chuk. Yes.Chuk double check that creature is not Chuk." />

            <br />

            <h3  style="padding-top: 15px">During Your Training</h3>
            <p>During your training you risked your life for something and were rewarded for it.</p>
