            </p>
            <input name="flags.detailedcharinfo.fivelessons5" value="{{flags.detailedcharinfo.fivelessons5}}" id="FiveLessons5" type="text" maxlength="300" placeholder="eg. Chuk cam very close but not dead. Chuk got tent back. Don't let bear take tent.'" />

