            <br />

            <h3  style="padding-top: 15px">Hidden Gems</h3>
            <p>Although there are hidden gems everywhere, most inns don't pride themselves on culinary delicacies.</p>
            <p>What do you always keep with you to liven up a bland meal?</p>
            <input name="flags.detailedcharinfo.flavor" value="{{flags.detailedcharinfo.flavor}}" id="flavor" type="text" maxlength="300" placeholder="eg. Chuk uses Chuk suace,secret recipie,Chuk will not reveal." />

            <br />

            <h3  style="padding-top: 15px">What Catches Your Eye</h3>
