            <p>What colorful thing cuts through the monotony of most inns?</p>
            <input name="flags.detailedcharinfo.color" value="{{flags.detailedcharinfo.color}}" id="color" type="text" maxlength="300" placeholder="eg. Chuk, likes the clothes of travlers they are always diffrent" />

            <br />

            <h3  style="padding-top: 15px">An Occasional Evening</h3>
